<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-font name="Red Hat Display" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Red+Hat+Display:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap"></mj-font>
    <mj-style>
      a {
        color: #4299e1;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .my-2 {
        margin-top: 2px;
        margin-bottom: 2px;
      }

      #summation-border {
        border-bottom: 1px solid #555;
        margin-top: 4px;
        margin-bottom: 4px
      }

      .block {
        display: block;
      }

      .text-black {
        color: #000;
      }

      .italic {
        font-style: italic
      }

      .font-bold {
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Red Hat Display', 'Arial'
      }
    </mj-style>

  </mj-head>
  <mj-body>
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column background-color="#ffffff">
        <mj-image width="420px" src="https://satstash.io/logo-black.png"></mj-image>

        <mj-divider border-color="#000000"></mj-divider>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">
          Your sale listing is live. Click <a href="{{ listingsListUrl }}">here to view, edit, or delete</a> any of your listings. Do <strong>NOT</strong> share this link with anyone.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">
          If you cancel your listing, your listing deposit will be immediately refunded by email as a Lightning enabled LNURL QR code (you may request the refund on Bitcoin mainchain). If you're not able to withdraw from the LNURL QR code, please reply with a Lightning invoice or address. Let us know if these options don't work for you and we'll send your refund via River Link through which you can withdraw over Lightning or onchain with applicable transaction fees.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">
          If someone buys the item, you will receive an email with shipping instructions. SatStash will release sale proceeds (minus a 10% commission fee, adjusted for your listing listing deposit) to the Bitcoin address you provide 3 days after delivery has been confirmed.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">
          You will lose your listing deposit under the following conditions:
        </mj-text>

        <mj-list>
          <mj-li font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">
            You attempt to list contraband. See this list for guidance.
          </mj-li>

          <mj-li font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">
            The item sells and you do not ship it within the allotted time.
          </mj-li>

          <mj-li font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">
            The delivered item does not match the listed item description.
          </mj-li>

          <mj-li font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">
            The item is damaged due to improper packaging. See our packaging requirements in the <a href="https://satstash.io/seller-guidelines">seller guidelines</a>. You will be asked to provide images of the packaging process or evidence that youâ€™ve hired a professional to pack the item.
          </mj-li>
        </mj-list>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">
          Buyers are asked to video record the unboxing of the item and we routinely route items through trusted parties for quality assurance.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">
          Please let us know if you have any questions.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Red Hat Display">Happy Selling,<br />
          <a href="https://satstash.io">
            SatStash
          </a>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>